<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">Even With a Wealth Tax, Economic Policy Ensures Billionaires Will Exist</h1>
</div>
</div>
</header>
<div class="row featured-media-block"><figure class="featured-media" itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject">
<noscript><img width="1200" height="675" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1118-hundred-dollar-bills-1200x675.jpg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="A man in a business suit counts out a fan of hundred dollar bills in his hands" itemprop="url" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1118-hundred-dollar-bills-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1118-hundred-dollar-bills-200x113.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1118-hundred-dollar-bills-400x225.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1118-hundred-dollar-bills-800x450.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1118-hundred-dollar-bills-2400x1350.jpg 2400w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px"></noscript><img width="1200" height="675" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%203%202'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="A man in a business suit counts out a fan of hundred dollar bills in his hands" itemprop="url" data-sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" data-srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1118-hundred-dollar-bills-1200x675.jpg 1200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1118-hundred-dollar-bills-200x113.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1118-hundred-dollar-bills-400x225.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1118-hundred-dollar-bills-800x450.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1118-hundred-dollar-bills-2400x1350.jpg 2400w" data-src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/2019_1118-hundred-dollar-bills-1200x675.jpg" loading="lazy">
<figcaption class="wp-caption-text" itemprop="caption">Within our current system, we can't minimize the voices of the superrich — but we can amplify the voices of the non-rich.</figcaption><figcaption class="wp-caption-credit" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name">Motortion / Getty Images</span></figcaption></figure></div>
